metadata.name: 𝔽𝕦𝕛𝕚𝕟【#𝟘𝟜】
metadata.description:
【風神/Fujin】
Fujin is a son whose father is "Izanagi" and mother is "Izanami".
He was born from the breath that Izanami blew off the morning mist.
Fujin is also called "Shinatsuhiko".

【Meaning】
“風 / fu” means ”wind”
“神 / jin” means “god”.

【Concept】
This art is inspired by the masterpiece of Japanese art, "Wind God and Thunder God".
Fuijin produces wind from a pouch behind him.
He is creating a gust of wind in the world of the Metaverse.
The relief on his back contains some elements of the Buddhist statue.
